name: AARAMBH 1.0 - IEEE AWARNESS PROGRAM
details: Aimed at fostering awareness of IEEE's global network, leadership pathways, and technical resources, this session featured key leaders:– @Suparna Kar Chowdhury, Chair, IEEE Kolkata Section– @Tridibesh Nag, Secretary, IEEE Kolkata Section & Vice Chair, IEEE India Council MDC– @Prof. Shila Ghosh, MDC, IEEE Kolkata Section

name: EV LOAD MODELLING TECHNIQUES - DISTINGUISHED LECTURE BY PROF. ATIF IQBAL
details: Delivered by Prof. Atif Iqbal (IEEE Fellow, Qatar University), the lecture addressed electric vehicle integration, charging impacts on grids, and smart modeling strategies—critical to the future of industrial electronics and energy systems.

name: IEEE IAS IEM STUDENTS CHAPTER INSTALLATION CEREMONY
details: The installation ceremony of the newly formed IEEE IES IEM Student Chapter was held on 5th August 2025 at the CII Auditorium, IEM Kolkata. The event marked the official launch of the chapter, featuring addresses by esteemed faculty and IEEE officials. It laid the foundation for a future of innovation, collaboration, and technical excellence.
